{"tid":557382,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"忠義街考車集氣區","createTime":"2018-02-11T09:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T04:02:34.000Z","uid":115613,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"366379194a5a4d1851e37ed6c1c70e680f3ecd94","tid":557382,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T09:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 二波入迦密村街果袋口位，如見只有一駕對頭車（假設1-2秒過得）<br />\n有沒巴打知用極加子+煞制慢慢袋口位停1-2秒再轉入去有沒問題，我知考車一定要一波起步<br />\n但用拉手制1波好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要等幾秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有沒大大pass過忠義街細圈指教下小弟<br />\n<br />\n利申<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細圈成日考但平時沒練開巧怕怕"},{"pid":"c249d81ddc6f1aea4e8c5ce849edd8151b8ba444","tid":557382,"uid":5278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"下 斜路黎喎"},{"pid":"d71d878f91f94deaa6e724bcb894bf031e82509a","tid":557382,"uid":10133,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T09:57:01.000Z","msg":"考車問師傅啦，上黎問把鬼咩"},{"pid":"75a68d22230c555551f9551840b8f12bd85dbf2f","tid":557382,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:08:33.000Z","msg":"短暫停車唔洗手制，不過停定一定要1波起步"},{"pid":"bfe16bf86f430c0c9b404a3521fcd20b0c262529","tid":557382,"uid":79627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75a68d22230c555551f9551840b8f12bd85dbf2f","tid":557382,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:08:33.000Z","msg":"短暫停車唔洗手制，不過停定一定要1波起步"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:09:39.000Z","msg":"*踩著極力子入返1波等，行得就放迫力行"},{"pid":"ae02394281fcb714442333bf307a73c1